# bt_api_bybit

Bybit exchange package for `bt_api`.

## Installation

```bash
pip install bt_api_bybit
```

## Usage

When installed alongside `bt_api_py`, the package is discovered automatically by the unified plugin loader.

## Supported Exchanges

- BYBIT___SPOT
- BYBIT___SWAP
